<view class="focus-page">
  <view class="focus-top">
    <button bindtap="backTimer">返回</button>
    <button bindtap="complete">退出并记录</button>
  </view>

  <view class="timer-center">
    <view class="phase">5 分钟沉浸</view>
    <view class="time large">{{timeText}}</view>
    <view class="focus-title">{{habit.title}}</view>
    <view class="focus-copy">这是额外延展，不是必须任务。现在结束也不会影响今天的完成。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="timer-actions">
    <button class="primary light" bindtap="complete">完成并记录</button>
    <button class="secondary dark" bindtap="moreFive">再来 5 分钟</button>
  </view>
</view>
